$interpreted: Clark: (Only ten days until the ship sets sail...if we don't start heading back within two days...)
Sherlock: You're blocking the light.
Clark: Sorry...I just want to know if you can fix Maria before the day after tomorrow?
Sherlock: You think a robot as intricate as this can be fixed up just like that!?
Clark: That's not what I meant...
Sherlock: What's more, a whole bunch of her parts have been utterly destroyed! Who did this to her!?
Clark: Sorry...
Clark: ...*sigh*...
Sherlock: Hey. Yeah, you. If you're pressed for time, why not leave her here for a bit?
Clark: Huh?
Sherlock: I think my daughter really likes her. Plus...
Sherlock: She'll be safer with me, don't ya think?
Clark: Um...
Sherlock: That way I can take my time fixing her. When you're finished with your business, you can come back to get her!
Clark: (If Maria stays with me, she'll probably keep running into danger...should I let her stay with Sherlock? I mean, he is a robot, just like her.)
Clark: (If something happens to her because of me, and she's damaged so badly that she can't be repaired...)
Sherlock: ...If you want to take her, that's fine too. But I can't tell you how many days it's going to take to fix her.
Clark: Will she be friends with Ned and Lisa?
Sherlock: Of course! My daughter'll look after her!
Clark: ...Okay. Please, take good care of her. Please tell her that when I'm finished with what I'm doing I'll come back for her.
Sherlock: Alright, alright, alright. Relax.
Clark: Hey! Don't eat that! That's the only food I've got left!
Clark: ...*sigh*...my sandwich.
Clark: Chu Chu?
Clark: You looking for Maria? Sorry, I forgot to leave you with her...
Chu Chu: ...*sob*...Chu...*sob*...Chu...Chu...
Clark: You miss her too?
Chu Chu: Chu! Chu!
Clark: ...*sigh*...you don't know what I'm saying, do you?
Chu Chu: Chu...
Clark: I wonder if Maria will be upset if she can't find me when she wakes up...
Chu Chu: Chu...
Clark: ......
Clark: Ouch!
Chu Chu: Chu Chu! ChuChuChuChuChu!!
Clark: ...She'll be just like you, won't she? Angry and upset.
Clark: I'm such an idiot. I need Chu Chu to explain something so obvious to me.
Clark: Chu Chu, let's go back and get Maria. Come on.
